name: The Long Caress Of Winter
description:
The foundation for this artwork was generated from AI that I trained with hundreds of my oil paintings, followed by my alterations and refinements using various digital tools. OIL + GAN + digital manipulation + remash with my paintings “Legend On Yesler” and “The Dark Tower Looms Over Night” and “The Awakening”.
David A. N. Cheifetz, 2021
4000 × 5130
